1817
02:07:31,930 --> 02:07:33,260
Any idea how is Shikha doing?

1818
02:07:34,330 --> 02:07:35,300
She'll be fine.

1819
02:07:36,820 --> 02:07:39,130
Even you'll be fine.
Everything will be all right, sir.

1820
02:07:40,450 --> 02:07:42,460
Everything appears to be fine, Tej.

1821
02:07:43,500 --> 02:07:45,200
But a few wounds never heal.

1822
02:07:47,240 --> 02:07:49,210
There are scars that stay
with us for our whole lives.

1823
02:07:53,820 --> 02:07:57,050
Anyway, all of us have to
write the debriefing reports.

1824
02:07:57,960 --> 02:08:00,280
