Drink some water.

1828
02:08:39,910 --> 02:08:41,200
Drink this water, Shikha.

1829
02:08:43,340 --> 02:08:45,190
Shikha, you need some water.
Drink it.

1830
02:08:47,740 --> 02:08:48,810
Come on.

1831
02:08:58,200 --> 02:09:01,970
