increased heartbeat...

1834
02:09:18,160 --> 02:09:20,320
Medically this is borderline PTSD.

1835
02:09:21,450 --> 02:09:23,000
Post-Traumatic Stress Disorder.

1836
02:09:24,040 --> 02:09:27,190
[Phone vibrating]

1837
02:09:31,030 --> 02:09:33,180
Shivalik is calling
again and again.

1838
02:09:35,220 --> 02:09:36,750
Won't you talk to him?

1839
02:09:39,710 --> 02:09:40,790
Look, Shikha.

1840
02:09:42,250 --> 02:09:46,100
As the RMO, I have to submit
my report to Colonel Sathe.

1841
02:09:46,770 --> 02:09:48,460
And after reading my reports...

1842
02:09:48,550 --> 02:09:51,450
...Col. Sathe might initiate
a court of enquiry.

1843
02:09:56,060 --> 02:09:57,890
I am asking you once again.

1844
02:09:59,740 --> 02:10:01,840
Is there anything
you want to tell me?

1845
02:10:05,050 --> 02:10:06,370
What happened over there?

1846
02:10:11,250 --> 02:10:12,210
[Bhatti] 'During Dozakh...'

1847
02:10:12,520 --> 02:10:15,390
...because of your good
or bad performance...

1848
02:10:15,480 --> 02:10:18,770
...your ranking on the
leader board might change.

1849
02:10:19,220 --> 02:10:20,460
You all must be aware...

1850
02:10:21,500 --> 02:10:24,410
...that Capt. Bilal won't
move ahead in this course.

1851
02:10:25,400 --> 02:10:28,570
For now, I want you...

1852
02:10:29,250 --> 02:10:32,270
...to write everything

1853
02:10:33,310 --> 02:10:36,660
in detail, in your debriefs.

1854
02:10:38,350 --> 02:10:40,780
Especially, Squad Alpha.

1855
02:10:43,700 --> 02:10:45,380
After all what happened
over there as such...

1856
02:10:46,210 --> 02:10:49,030
...that Capt. Siddiqui and
Capt. Shikha Sharma got injured?

1857
02:10:52,050 --> 02:10:53,190
Sir.

1858
02:10:53,760 --> 02:10:55,660
But our two buddies
are in the hospital.

1859
02:10:57,820 --> 02:10:59,440
Capt. Bilal has been informed.

1860
02:11:00,320 --> 02:11:02,310
He will submit the
report before leaving.

1861
02:11:04,530 --> 02:11:07,010
Capt. Shikha will submit
her report once she recovers.

1862
02:11:14,330 --> 02:11:15,310
Anything else?

1863
02:11:17,690 --> 02:11:19,330
So, come on.
Write down.

1864
02:12:25,300 --> 02:12:28,410
Sir, I wrote what I could recall.

1865
02:12:33,390 --> 02:12:37,050
