1867
02:12:39,620 --> 02:12:43,450
And volunteer again
for the SFTC next year.

1868
02:12:44,780 --> 02:12:47,350
Mr. Naved will help
you fill your exit form.

1869
02:12:49,230 --> 02:12:51,840
Do inform me,
if you need something.

1870
02:13:17,000 --> 02:13:19,470
[Phone ringing]

1871
02:13:21,730 --> 02:13:22,650
Capt. Rao.

1872
02:13:23,290 --> 02:13:24,350
Yes, sir.

1873
02:13:24,600 --> 02:13:25,600
