1874
02:13:27,370 --> 02:13:28,510
Yes, sir.

1875
02:13:28,880 --> 02:13:31,740
I'll be submitting my reports
in the next couple of days.

1876
02:13:33,780 --> 02:13:35,660
Yes, sir.
Right.

1877
02:13:45,640 --> 02:13:49,630
