fellow officer in SFTC.

1891
02:15:41,840 --> 02:15:43,370
It is not possible.

1892
02:15:43,890 --> 02:15:44,760
In fact, till date

1893
02:15:44,850 --> 02:15:46,900
no such incident has taken place
in any of our training academies.

1894
02:15:46,960 --> 02:15:49,300
Till date, men and women officers
were never trained together...

1895
02:15:49,380 --> 02:15:51,840
...at the same place, Bedi.

1896
02:15:53,270 --> 02:15:54,520
