defamed for sure.

1901
02:16:04,580 --> 02:16:06,010
For now, only we have
received this mail.

1902
02:16:06,250 --> 02:16:09,410
What if it is sent
to a news channel?

1903
02:16:09,890 --> 02:16:11,640
Someday there is going to be
a witch-hunt at prime time.

1904
02:16:11,720 --> 02:16:12,570
Heads will roll.

1905
02:16:12,760 --> 02:16:13,940
[Phone ringing]

1906
02:16:14,460 --> 02:16:15,770
Damn it.

1907
02:16:19,670 --> 02:16:21,120
