catch up with everyone.

1930
02:17:42,890 --> 02:17:46,670
Actually, it will
be really difficult.

1931
02:17:48,590 --> 02:17:52,760
And I don't want the future
of a good officer to be damaged.

1932
02:17:54,530 --> 02:17:56,150
If you want to leave now...

1933
02:17:57,350 --> 02:18:00,560
...I will not consider
you as a failure.

1934
02:18:03,370 --> 02:18:04,370
I mean it.

1935
02:18:08,840 --> 02:18:12,120
In fact, if you would like
to volunteer next year...

1936
02:18:12,210 --> 02:18:14,150
...I myself will recommend you.

1937
02:18:19,220 --> 02:18:20,380
But...

1938
02:18:20,660 --> 02:18:24,870
...the final decision
is going to be yours.

1939
02:18:26,410 --> 02:18:28,230
[Bedi] 'Has any official
complaint been lodged yet?'

1940
02:18:28,320 --> 02:18:29,520
Not yet.

1941
02:18:30,660 --> 02:18:33,000
But maybe the complaint
has been suppressed.

1942
02:18:33,090 --> 02:18:35,360
Stop spinning
conspiracy theories, Raman.

1943
02:18:35,550 --> 02:18:37,050
Sathe can't do that.

1944
02:18:38,480 --> 02:18:39,600
Bedi.

1945
