1947
02:18:43,740 --> 02:18:47,160
One such incident
can finish his career.

1948
02:19:20,510 --> 02:19:22,280
[Phone ringing]

1949
02:19:22,610 --> 02:19:23,680
Good morning, sir.

1950
02:19:24,230 --> 02:19:26,320
