the stakes are really high.

1959
02:19:45,160 --> 02:19:48,360
So, just keep me updated.

1960
02:19:49,480 --> 02:19:50,430
Yes, sir.

1961
02:19:55,510 --> 02:19:57,290
Either Sathe is
concealing the truth...

1962
02:19:57,370 --> 02:19:59,180
...or he genuinely
doesn't know anything.

1963
02:19:59,660 --> 02:20:01,030
We don't have time
to do guesswork...

1964
02:20:01,160 --> 02:20:02,530
...sitting in Delhi.

1965
02:20:02,810 --> 02:20:04,200
You mean another official enquiry.

1966
02:20:04,290 --> 02:20:05,560
Exactly.

1967
02:20:06,150 --> 02:20:08,130
But we have only 3 weeks.

1968
02:20:09,480 --> 02:20:11,650
We need someone
who can go there...

1969
02:20:11,740 --> 02:20:15,730
...and check all the facts in
an unbiased and objective way.

1970
02:20:16,590 --> 02:20:20,010
Someone whom we can trust.

1971
02:20:21,400 --> 02:20:23,200
Since you have already
given all this a thought...

1972
02:20:23,290 --> 02:20:26,630
...tell me, who is going
to lead this investigation?

1973
02:20:26,720 --> 02:20:30,550
Well, someone whom
I implicitly trust.

1974
02:20:31,250 --> 02:20:33,090
There is only one officer
in my mind.

1975
02:20:33,380 --> 02:20:35,910
Someone who can call
a spade, a spade.

1976
02:20:36,390 --> 02:20:38,700
- Imtiyaz Hussain.
- Literally?

1977
02:20:39,660 --> 02:20:40,990
Your poker champ?

1978
02:20:42,280 --> 02:20:45,430
In such a short time,
no one else can do this work.

1979
02:20:46,590 --> 02:20:48,840
I agree that his
ways are different.

1980
02:20:49,270 --> 02:20:50,390
But you know what?

1981
02:20:50,520 --> 02:20:53,070
Nine times out of ten, they work.

1982
02:20:54,090 --> 02:20:56,320
Okay. Let's hope
for all our sake...

1983
02:20:56,800 --> 02:20:59,710
