1992
02:21:36,320 --> 02:21:38,380
then how do you lose
against me and mom?

1993
02:21:39,300 --> 02:21:40,530
Dear, you are a champ.

1994
02:21:40,620 --> 02:21:43,440
And your mom is a
bigger champ than you.

1995
02:21:43,530 --> 02:21:45,920
No one could defeat
your mom till date.

1996
02:21:47,050 --> 02:21:49,100
-[Mallika] Immi.
- Yeah. Coming.

1997
02:21:49,190 --> 02:21:52,660
You know I always win
