3025
03:27:03,140 --> 03:27:05,870
[Gunshots]

3026
03:27:06,540 --> 03:27:07,810
[Fan sound]

3027
03:27:11,820 --> 03:27:12,870
[Gunshots]

3028
03:27:16,860 --> 03:27:17,700
[Whistle]

3029
03:27:19,990 --> 03:27:22,450
[Gunshots]

3030
03:27:25,720 --> 03:27:28,620
[Gunshots]

3031
03:27:34,240 --> 03:27:35,050
[Gunshot]

3032
03:27:44,480 --> 03:27:48,070
[Gunshots]

3033
03:27:55,140 --> 03:27:58,470
[Gunshots]

3034
03:28:00,080 --> 03:28:03,840
[Gunshots]

3035
03:28:17,090 --> 03:28:17,980
[Gunshot]

3036
03:28:32,830 --> 03:28:34,070
Hello, Capt. Shikha.

3037
03:28:34,940 --> 03:28:37,040
Your wrist must be hurting
after Krav Maga bout.

3038
03:28:37,710 --> 03:28:39,200
That's why you
missed the shot as well.

3039
03:28:39,930 --> 03:28:41,690
It's okay.
Happens.

3040
03:28:43,090 --> 03:28:45,480
Actually, Manit, you are
a cross country runner.

3041
03:28:45,690 --> 03:28:46,810
You think one step at a time.

3042
03:28:47,430 --> 03:28:48,810
I think about future.

3043
03:28:50,780 --> 03:28:52,640
It's too deep.
You won't understand.

3044
03:28:58,300 --> 03:28:59,300
[Manit] 'Yes, sir.'

3045
03:28:59,750 --> 03:29:00,840
Yes, sir.
I know, sir.

3046
03:29:01,230 --> 03:29:02,430
Thank you very much, sir.

3047
03:29:02,510 --> 03:29:03,560
I really appreciate it.

3048
03:29:03,710 --> 03:29:04,730
Thank you.

3049
03:29:04,920 --> 03:29:06,050
What happened, dude?

3050
03:29:06,730 --> 03:29:09,070
You seem really happy.

3051
03:29:09,850 --> 03:29:11,780
Do you remember about my brawl
I had during my YO's course?

3052
03:29:11,870 --> 03:29:14,780
Yes, you told me. It's was
your ex-girlfriend's issue.

3053
03:29:16,020 --> 03:29:18,450
That got solved.
How?

3054
03:29:19,020 --> 03:29:22,850
- It was a false complaint.
- You're tactical, s**le.

3055
03:29:22,940 --> 03:29:24,520
That is why I'm at number one
on the leader board.

3056
03:29:24,830 --> 03:29:25,970
Number one.

3057
03:29:26,140 --> 03:29:27,260
Good.

3058
03:29:29,230 --> 03:29:34,010
[Gunshots]

3059
03:29:39,890 --> 03:29:41,260
[Imtiyaz] 'Close shot
there, Capt. Sharma.'

3060
03:29:42,820 --> 03:29:43,910
What do you mean, sir?

3061
03:29:44,650 --> 03:29:46,890
I mean to say, you were right.

3062
03:29:48,250 --> 03:29:49,370
About what, sir?

3063
03:29:49,590 --> 03:29:51,650
That you don't need me.

3064
03:29:51,840 --> 03:29:53,990
You are the hero of your story.

3065
03:29:55,400 --> 03:29:58,350
I know you missed
the last shot deliberately.

3066
03:29:59,070 --> 03:30:00,550
During the final exercise...

3067
03:30:00,680 --> 03:30:03,520
...rank one and rank three
will be paired. You knew it.

3068
03:30:04,170 --> 03:30:06,300
That's why you went to
number three from number two.

3069
03:30:07,430 --> 03:30:08,620
Why would I do that, sir?

3070
03:30:08,700 --> 03:30:10,910
In order to end
what Manit had started.

3071
03:30:13,810 --> 03:30:15,010
I know the truth.

3072
03:30:22,500 --> 03:30:24,870
Sir, my truth is that...

3073
03:30:26,420 --> 03:30:27,970
...I am in the special forces...

3074
03:30:28,060 --> 03:30:30,590
...because I deserve
to be in the special forces, sir.

3075
03:30:32,250 --> 03:30:34,890
Not because of my gender
or in spite of being a girl.

3076
03:30:37,340 --> 03:30:38,520
I am a soldier's daughter, sir.

3077
03:30:38,720 --> 03:30:39,880
I am an athlete.

3078
03:30:39,940 --> 03:30:41,040
A shooting champion.

3079
03:30:41,200 --> 03:30:42,840
Since childhood,
I always had one dream...

3080
03:30:42,920 --> 03:30:45,780
...that I would wear this uniform
after I grow up.

3081
03:30:47,700 --> 03:30:51,270
And no feudal...

3082
03:30:51,970 --> 03:30:53,300
...misogynistic...

3083
03:30:54,660 --> 03:30:57,030
...criminal, unofficer like man...

3084
03:30:58,280 --> 03:31:00,520
...can neither snatch away
this dream of mine, sir...

3085
03:31:00,600 --> 03:31:02,320
...nor my sense of justice.

3086
03:31:02,960 --> 03:31:04,090
Let's get the past done.

3087
03:31:04,170 --> 03:31:05,700
Sir, I had already told you...

3088
03:31:07,240 --> 03:31:08,320
...I am enough for myself.

3089
03:31:11,240 --> 03:31:12,310
Shikha.

3090
03:31:16,050 --> 03:31:18,560
Think about others
and not just yourself.

3091
03:31:21,410 --> 03:31:23,410
Other lady officers
will come after you.

3092
03:31:23,490 --> 03:31:25,190
We must set an example for them.

3093
03:31:25,700 --> 03:31:27,360
- And defence minister...
- Defence minister...

3094
03:31:27,440 --> 03:31:28,960
...whose poster girl I am, sir.

3095
03:31:30,700 --> 03:31:32,110
I maybe her poster girl...

3096
03:31:32,590 --> 03:31:35,940
...but I am not her or any
politician's puppet, sir.

3097
03:31:38,010 --> 03:31:39,440
As for all the lady officers...

3098
03:31:39,520 --> 03:31:42,800
...then I am trying to set
an example for them, sir.

3099
03:31:43,720 --> 03:31:44,550
Till now...

3100
03:31:44,650 --> 03:31:47,680
...why weren't girls inducted
into the Indian Special Forces?

3101
03:31:48,980 --> 03:31:51,730
The authorities have their
reasons and they are valid.

3102
03:31:53,150 --> 03:31:56,870
This is my only opportunity
to prove them wrong.

3103
03:31:58,350 --> 03:32:00,410
I deserve to die
for this country...

3104
03:32:00,500 --> 03:32:02,460
...as much as any man.

3105
03:32:03,600 --> 03:32:05,800
The lady officers will
come here in future...

3106
03:32:05,880 --> 03:32:08,340
...because we will earn
our right to be here.

3107
03:32:10,670 --> 03:32:12,750
If I fail in this test now, sir...

3108
03:32:14,610 --> 03:32:16,030
...the door of active
combat will be closed...

3109
03:32:16,190 --> 03:32:19,240
...for thousands of girls.

3110
03:32:19,310 --> 03:32:20,710
And you won't let that happen.

3111
03:32:22,500 --> 03:32:24,500
I'm happy that you are looking
at the larger picture.

3112
03:32:25,130 --> 03:32:26,680
In fact, I respect you for that.

3113
03:32:27,690 --> 03:32:30,560
But still we must name and
shame the b*****d, Shikha.

3114
03:32:32,650 --> 03:32:33,730
I...

3115
03:32:34,640 --> 03:32:35,740
Not we, sir.

3116
03:32:41,690 --> 03:32:43,690
In my 26 years of career...

3117
03:32:44,680 --> 03:32:46,490
...I turned out to be
wrong for the first time.

3118
03:32:47,810 --> 03:32:50,590
Imtiyaz, give me
that officer's name.

3119
03:32:51,480 --> 03:32:53,210
He does not deserve
the maroon beret.

3120
03:32:56,950 --> 03:32:58,950
Sometimes to figure out
the opponent's game...

3121
03:32:59,560 --> 03:33:01,140
...we have to call all
the bets on the table.

3122
03:33:06,640 --> 03:33:08,600
But these are rankings
for tomorrow's exercise.

3123
03:33:09,170 --> 03:33:10,270
Yes.

3124
03:33:10,860 --> 03:33:12,820
Shikha has come to number
three from number two.

3125
03:33:12,980 --> 03:33:16,360
Which means her buddy has
been changed in the final exercise.

3126
03:33:21,380 --> 03:33:22,800
God d**m it.

3127
03:33:24,270 --> 03:33:25,480
Capt. Manit!

3128
03:33:27,600 --> 03:33:29,610
I'm going to roger that fellow.

3129
03:33:29,680 --> 03:33:30,850
But not now, sir.

3130
03:33:31,940 --> 03:33:32,750
What do you mean?

3131
03:33:34,830 --> 03:33:38,700
It's my honour, my self-respect.

3132
03:33:39,820 --> 03:33:41,550
In order to protect this...

3133
03:33:42,350 --> 03:33:45,330
...I don't need
the help of any man.

3134
03:33:48,840 --> 03:33:50,890
- But, Shikha...
- I won't complain, sir.

3135
03:33:52,440 --> 03:33:53,950
He will confess.

3136
03:33:55,130 --> 03:33:56,320
But, Shikha, still...

3137
03:33:56,400 --> 03:33:57,830
Please give me 24 hours.

3138
03:33:58,790 --> 03:34:02,230
Just 24 hours.
Please.

3139
03:34:04,200 --> 03:34:05,800
[Sathe] 'This is absurd, Imtiyaz.'

3140
03:34:06,010 --> 03:34:07,970
Manit needs to be
thrown out right away.

3141
03:34:08,150 --> 03:34:10,340
But sir, you won't be able to
do this without my report.

3142
03:34:11,530 --> 03:34:15,300
Don't teach me what
I can and can't do.

3143
03:34:22,740 --> 03:34:24,200
Just 24 hours, sir.

3144
03:34:25,290 --> 03:34:28,120
Shikha has asked me and I
am asking you. Please, sir.

3145
03:34:29,310 --> 03:34:31,820
You'll get Manit's confession
in these 24 hours.

3146
03:34:35,150 --> 03:34:36,890
Lieutenant colonel
Imtiyaz Hussain...

3147
03:34:38,200 --> 03:34:42,760
...if Manit commits another act
of injustice in these 24 hours...

3148
03:34:43,950 --> 03:34:46,120
...will you take the
responsibility for it?

3149
03:34:47,130 --> 03:34:49,690
I'm turning the situation
on its head.

3150
03:34:51,030 --> 03:34:55,330
What will we do if Shikha
takes a severe step?

3151
03:34:56,250 --> 03:34:59,190
Sir, Shikha came so far
just because of her ability.

3152
03:34:59,720 --> 03:35:01,990
You had no hopes
from her on day one.

3153
03:35:02,150 --> 03:35:03,290
But today...

3154
03:35:03,420 --> 03:35:06,160
Just give her one chance
on this last day.

3155
03:35:06,770 --> 03:35:10,040
Then you will get both the
complaint and the confession.

3156
03:35:10,120 --> 03:35:11,840
And that's my promise to you, sir.

3157
03:35:14,330 --> 03:35:15,630
Now, she isn't the test case, sir.

3158
03:35:16,290 --> 03:35:18,140
In fact, she is the best case.

3159
03:35:18,760 --> 03:35:20,960
Don't think as a commandant.
Think like a soldier, sir.

3160
03:35:21,850 --> 03:35:25,040
And Shikha is a soldier
who deserves her justice.

3161
03:35:36,120 --> 03:35:37,950
[Phone ringing]

3162
03:35:38,400 --> 03:35:40,230
- Yes, Mom.
- It's the last chance

3163
03:35:40,520 --> 03:35:41,740
and you have to come first.

3164
03:35:41,830 --> 03:35:43,490
- Or else...
- You'll break my legs, right?

3165
03:35:44,180 --> 03:35:45,310
[Shikha] 'I know that, Mom.'

3166
03:35:45,750 --> 03:35:46,740
I don't know about coming first.

3167
03:35:46,820 --> 03:35:49,000
But I will finish what I started.

3168
03:35:50,220 --> 03:35:51,530
[Shikha] 'Dad must
have gone somewhere.'

3169
03:35:54,690 --> 03:35:55,800
Yes, dear.

3170
03:35:56,600 --> 03:35:59,630
- Forget it.
- Dear, we all are with you.

3171
03:36:00,150 --> 03:36:01,160
Just wait and watch...

3172
03:36:01,350 --> 03:36:03,300
...you will be the number one.

3173
03:36:04,410 --> 03:36:06,490
I'll call you after the exercise,
Mom. Okay?

3174
03:36:07,720 --> 03:36:09,000
Take care of yourself.

3175
03:36:09,680 --> 03:36:10,600
Bye, Mom.

3176
03:36:30,220 --> 03:36:32,140
[Door knocking]

3177
03:36:37,890 --> 03:36:39,110
[Gunshot]

3178
03:36:49,380 --> 03:36:50,990
Going beyond enemy lines...

3179
03:36:51,190 --> 03:36:55,390
...is a part and parcel of every
special officer's life.

3180
03:36:56,650 --> 03:36:57,760
But...

3181
03:36:58,520 --> 03:37:03,410
...our work is not just to cross
the border and kill our enemies.

3182
03:37:04,300 --> 03:37:07,840
Many times, we need
to rescue the hostages.

3183
03:37:08,210 --> 03:37:10,730
Be it civilians,
political prisoners...

3184
03:37:10,820 --> 03:37:13,170
...or our own soldiers.

3185
03:37:13,760 --> 03:37:17,660
Your last exercise is
hostage rescue operation.

3186
03:37:18,960 --> 03:37:20,290
Lieutenant Colonel Imtiyaz.

3187
03:37:22,470 --> 03:37:25,730
Officers, you will perform
this task in pairs of two.

3188
03:37:25,840 --> 03:37:28,840
You need to cross the border
and enter the enemy area.

3189
03:37:28,920 --> 03:37:32,620
And without using any ammunition,
you have to rescue the hostages.

3190
03:37:32,850 --> 03:37:34,390
And in the heat of the moment...

3191
03:37:34,470 --> 03:37:36,250
...if you use ammunition...

3192
03:37:36,330 --> 03:37:37,850
...you will be disqualified.

3193
03:37:39,300 --> 03:37:40,430
Dummy hostage...

3194
03:37:40,710 --> 03:37:43,650
...can be anywhere among
these five locations.

3195
03:37:44,760 --> 03:37:48,600
And if the enemy traces you in
the process or if you get caught...

3196
03:37:49,750 --> 03:37:51,610
...you will be out
of this exercise.

3197
03:37:52,440 --> 03:37:53,970
And if you are able to cross
the border...

3198
03:37:54,110 --> 03:37:55,740
...you will regroup at Point Alpha.

3199
03:37:56,090 --> 03:37:57,980
In order to complete this task...

3200
03:37:58,120 --> 03:38:00,820
...very buddy pair
will have just two hours' time.

3201
03:38:02,930 --> 03:38:03,950
Remember one thing.

3202
03:38:04,870 --> 03:38:06,320
Your real weapon...

3203
03:38:07,160 --> 03:38:08,780
...is your sharp mind and body.

3204
03:38:10,530 --> 03:38:11,620
So, get ready.

3205
03:38:16,220 --> 03:38:17,850
Just don't slow me down,
Capt. Sharma.

3206
03:38:19,160 --> 03:38:20,610
Want to finish with the flourish.

3207
03:38:21,390 --> 03:38:23,380
Don't worry, Capt. Manit.
You will finish...

3208
03:38:23,610 --> 03:38:24,610
...with a flourish.

3209
03:38:26,320 --> 03:38:27,410
[Bhatti] 'Attention.'

3210
03:38:28,020 --> 03:38:29,180
Are you people ready?

3211
03:38:29,210 --> 03:38:30,890
Yes, sir...
- [Whistle]

3212
03:38:31,240 --> 03:38:33,990
[Boots thumping]

3213
03:38:46,570 --> 03:38:47,760
[Wire cutting]

3214
