[Footsteps]

3218
03:39:52,480 --> 03:39:53,560
[Door opening]

3219
03:39:54,570 --> 03:39:55,890
[Gun cocking]

3220
03:39:59,640 --> 03:40:01,350
[Footsteps]
- [Gun cocking]

3221
03:40:04,260 --> 03:40:06,140
[Man falling]

3222
03:40:11,250 --> 03:40:12,710
[Man kicking]

3223
03:40:29,410 --> 03:40:30,490
[Pliers snipping]

3224
03:40:41,460 --> 03:40:42,580
[Gun cocking]

3225
03:40:50,330 --> 03:40:51,900
[Kicking]

3226
03:41:25,560 --> 03:41:30,260
[Footsteps]

3227
03:42:06,500 --> 03:42:08,610
[Huffing]

3228
03:42:13,290 --> 03:42:15,990
I specifically told you not
to slow me down, Capt. Sharma.

3229
03:42:21,160 --> 03:42:22,250
Slow you down!

3230
03:42:23,510 --> 03:42:24,930
You are here because of me.

3231
03:42:26,880 --> 03:42:28,290
Who saved your life a while ago?

3232
03:42:30,050 --> 03:42:31,430
S***a coward.

3233
03:42:31,500 --> 03:42:33,450
You no more address me
with respect.

3234
03:42:35,510 --> 03:42:36,580
Really?

3235
03:42:38,500 --> 03:42:41,860
Will you declare to the whole world
that you saved my life?

3236
03:42:43,350 --> 03:42:46,360
And you didn't save my life.
I was handling myself.

3237
03:42:47,510 --> 03:42:49,500
I was not asking for help,
like you girls.

3238
03:42:51,610 --> 03:42:54,530
Girls will only ask for help
when guys like you are with them.

3239
03:42:55,660 --> 03:42:56,940
What the f**k!

3240
03:42:57,410 --> 03:42:59,910
Unfortunately, this is army
and not a kitty party.

3241
03:43:00,130 --> 03:43:01,730
There are no points
for bitching here.

3242
03:43:07,100 --> 03:43:08,310
You know, this...

3243
03:43:09,350 --> 03:43:12,210
This is exactly why girls
shouldn't be inducted into SF.

3244
03:43:13,030 --> 03:43:14,750
It's fine to be doctors and nurses.

3245
03:43:15,720 --> 03:43:18,510
But active combat
is not your cup of tea.

3246
03:43:19,600 --> 03:43:22,080
You come here professing
your love for the country.

